videoDetails.title: "I May Fall" Lyrics - RWBY Volume 3 - Jeff Williams ft. Casey Lee Williams & Lamar Hall
videoDetails.shortDescription:
There's a blessing in the CRWBY using a V1 song for a scene in V3... not having to wait till the V3 soundtrack comes out to see the lyric video! Enjoy my lyric video of "I May Fall" to Velvet kicking ass, and remember to support RWBY by buying the song on iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/rwby-vol.-1-soundtrack/id785720869
**RWBY and its music is the property of Rooster Teeth Productions, LLC. This video is for entertainment purposes only and has not been monetized.**
